These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, cycling
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, indian
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, sports
1. the person watching action movies is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
2. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the egyptian##5
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | coffee      |
| Sport          | cycling | soccer    |
| Nationality         | indian   | egyptian |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | sports      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, aristoff
2 different games are played: poker, go
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
3. the person playing go is not to the right of the person playing poker##8
4. the person driving the boat is not the aristoff-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea    |
| Cigar       | ritmeester         | aristoff |
| Game         | go | poker   |
| Transport   | boat               | snowmobile  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
