2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, cain
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, balloon-flower
2 different pets are kept: cat, ferret
1. the person who growsdahlia is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | thriller |
| Cigar   | chaman       | cain    |
| Flower   | dahlia | balloon-flower |
| Pet           | cat        | ferret   |

